Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
delete_cell_stack_area(25.10)                    delete_cell_stack_area(25.10)

Name
       delete_cell_stack_area - Deletes the cell stack area definition

Syntax
       delete_cell_stack_area

       [-help]

       [-cell <cell_name>]

       [-group <group_name>]

       Deletes the cell stack area definition.

Parameters
       -cell <cell_name>
              Specifies  the  cell(s) for which the cell stack area definition
              needs to be deleted.

       -group <group_name>
              Specifies the group(s) for which the cell stack area  definition
              needs to be deleted.

       -help  Outputs  a  brief description that includes type and default in-
              formation for each delete_cell_stack_area parameter.

              For a detailed description of the command and all of its parame-
              ters, use the man command: man delete_cell_stack_area

Related Information
              * report_cell_stack_area

              * specify_cell_stack_area

